# Deploy Connector

> **Status: stub — implementation pending.** Contract only. Consolidates the
> deploy steps across `create-connector`, `add-connector-oauth`, and the
> two-PR promotion discipline from `migrate-connector-to-arrow`.

## Purpose

Get the connector running: quick-publish the image, `terraform apply` to
dev, and — after dev is verified — promote to prod. This skill owns the
applies that the scaffold/provision skills deliberately left un-run.

Phase: **deploy/verify**.

## Inputs (from connector-spec.yaml)

- `slug` — image, service, and resource names.
- `stages` — the dev → prod promotion order.
- `delivery.path` — Arrow migrations follow two-PR discipline.

## Outputs

- Deployed dev and (after promotion) prod services.

## Human gates

- **quick-publish force-push**, **`terraform apply` dev**, and **prod
  promotion** are each hard human gates, confirmed per stage.
- **Two-PR discipline** where it applies: add-then-verify before any
  delete/cutover; no fix-forward across a correctness gate.
- Prod is never applied before `/verify-connector` passes on dev.

